digiKam 8.9.0 - Release date: 2026-03-xx

*****************************************************************************************************
NEW FEATURES:

Bundles component versions:

(*): Updated compared to previous digiKam release.

| Bundles       | Qt version | KDE version | OpenCV version | FFmpeg version | Heif version | ExifTool version | Exiv2 version |
|---------------|------------|-------------|----------------|----------------|--------------|------------------|---------------|
| Windows Qt5   | 5.15.17    | 5.116       | 4.11           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.2       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |
| Windows Qt6   | 6.9.1      | 6.17.0      | 4.11           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.2       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |
| AppImage Qt5  | 5.15.17    | 5.116       | 4.12           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.1       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |
| AppImage Qt6  | 6.9.1      | 6.17.0      | 4.12           | 7.1.1          | 1.20.1       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |
| macOS Qt5     | 5.15.15    | 5.116       | 4.12           | 7.1.1          | 1.19.8       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |
| macOS Qt6     | 6.9.1      | 6.17.0      | 4.12           | 7.1.1          | 1.19.8       | 13.40 (*)        | 0.25.5        |

RawEngine      : Update internal Libraw to last 20251026 upstream.
AdvancedRename : New modifier "Date Format".


